  <content>
Draws diagrams using [Mermaid](https://mermaid.js.org/)

== Example ==

{{code language="none"}}
{{mermaid}}
graph LR
    A --- B
    B--&gt;C[fa:fa-ban forbidden]
    B--&gt;D(fa:fa-spinner);
{{/mermaid}}
{{/code}}

Generates:

{{mermaid}}
graph LR
    A --- B
    B--&gt;C[fa:fa-ban forbidden]
    B--&gt;D(fa:fa-spinner);
{{/mermaid}}

  </content>
